Installation instructions for AlsaMixer.app


Requirements
-------------------------------------------------------------------
- X11, libxpm (devel version of both), libpulse (devel version),
        C++ development environment
        Most (Linux) systems have these things installed by default.
        If you don't have it look for packages that fit your
        distribution (especially somelib-devel packages).


Installation
-------------------------------------------------------------------
1) make
2) su
3) make install       (to put it in /usr/local/GNUstep/Apps/PulseMixer.app)
   or
   make install-x11   (to put it in /usr/bin)
5) exit


Running
-------------------------------------------------------------------
To run this program:
/usr/local/GNUstep/Apps/PulseMixer.app/PulseMixer.a[[]] &
or
/usr/bin/PulseMixer.app &


For more information about available command line arguments:
/usr/local/GNUstep/Apps/PulseMixer.app/PulseMixer.app --help
or
/usr/bin/PulseMixer.app --help
